%description
This is a configuration plugin for Git repo/branch information. A
configuration plugin is sort of like a Stash, but is better suited for intra-
plugin data sharing, using distro (not user) data.

%prep
%setup -q -n Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Config-Git-%{version}

